originalText.text: Ms. Sousa has been my life coach for quite some time and I’m the better for it.  She is able to help you find a pleasant medium between family struggles, work life stress, love life debacles and any other issues you might be having a tough time with. Her professionalism is impeccable. She has made a long lasting impact to my life.
